enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve setting and comparing error codes, which are central to the functionality of the ErrorCodeAttribute class.
The equals method compares the error class, which is set by the setErrorClass method.
The equals method compares the error number, which is set by the setErrorNumber method.
The equals method compares the error code, which is retrieved by the getErrorCode method.
The equals method compares the error class, which is retrieved by the getErrorClass method.
The equals method compares the error number, which is retrieved by the getErrorNumber method.
The equals method compares the reason phrase, which is retrieved by the getReasonPhrase method.
